MC is a Health Department programme. It: I-MC uhlelo loMnyango Wezempilo. Luthumela i-SMS ngawe nengane yakho. Ukubona, ukushintsha, ukusula ulwazi lwakho, shaya *134*550*7#
MomConnect needs your personal info to s: IMomConnect idinga ulwazi lwakho ukuthumela imiyalezo ngesigaba sokukhulelwa noma ngokukhula kwengane yakho. Ukwazi ukuthi ubhalisaphi kusiza uMnyango Wezempilo usebenze ngezincomo noma izikhalo ongazithumelela i-MomConnect ngeklinikhi lakho.
MomConnect collects your phone and ID nu: I-MomConnect iqoqa izinombolo zakho zefoni neze-ID, indawo yeklinikhi, nolwazi ngokukhulelwa kwakho.
MomConnect is owned and run by the Healt: I-MomConnect eyoMnyango Wezempilo. U-MTN, Cell C, Telkom, Praekelt, Jembi ne-HISP baqoqela futhi bawuqhubele ulwazi lwakho.

MomConnect will automatically delete you: I-MomConnect izozisulela ulwazi lakho emuva kweminyaka ewu-7 nezinyanga eziwu-9 ubhalisile.
